 Answer is -LRB- C -RRB-; correctly answered by 95 percent of test-takers. `` MAGNANIMOUS'' -LRB- A -RRB- dainty -LRB- B -RRB- latent -LRB- C -RRB- vengeful -LRB- D -RRB- conspicuous -LRB- E -RRB- compatible
</TEXT>
