 <PERSON> Michael </PERSON> <PERSON> Norton </PERSON> is based in <LOCATION> Port-au-Prince </LOCATION> as correspondent for <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> and has lived in <LOCATION> Haiti </LOCATION> for the past two years.
