<HEAD>Fire Jumps Line, Moves to Outskirts Of City, 500 Flee</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 8 grafs to update with today's situation, CORRECT
that state saying seven, sted nine, homes burned; picks up 9th
graf, `Along Interstate...' Subs 13th graf, `In Montana...' to
update with today's status. Subs 17th graf, `The Vacaville...' to
