<HEAD>U.S. Ambassador To Mongolia Presents Credentials _ Then Leaves</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By KATHY WILHELM</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>BEIJING (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
